OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FA special constable inappropriately
OL,7,Fviewed graphic and distressing images
OL,8,Fof two students killed by Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane, including footage of their
OL,10,Fbodies being placed into body bags.
OL,12,FSc Ilsadin Skenderaj is the only
OL,13,Fpolice officer or member of staff
OL,14,Fknown to have accessed footage linked
OL,15,Fto the Nottingham attacks that they
OL,16,Fshould not have viewed, the inquiry
OL,17,Fwas told on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
