OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FValdo Calocane killed two University
OL,7,Fof Nottingham students, Grace O'Malley
OL,8,FKumar and Barnaby Webber in June 2023,
OL,9,Fas well as school caretaker Ian Coates.
OL,11,FThree people, Wayne Birkett, Sharon
OL,12,FMiller and Marcin Gawronski also
OL,13,Fsustained serious injuries but
OL,14,Fsurvived after they were hit by
OL,15,FCalocane driving Ian Coates' van.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FDuring evidence from the head of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police's Professional
OL,8,FStandards Directorate (PSD),
OL,9,FSuperintendent Kathryn Craner, counsel
OL,10,Fto the inquiry Alex Ivory said
OL,11,FSkenderaj had self-reported that he
OL,12,Fhad viewed footage in September 2023.
OL,14,FMr Ivory said Skenderaj was found to
OL,15,Fhave viewed 12 separate recordings,
OL,16,Fincluding Calocane's arrest, and had
OL,17,F"offensively and hurtfully" viewed
OL,18,Ffootage filmed within an ambulance.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FThe footage viewed by the special
OL,7,Fconstable showed officers and
OL,8,Fparamedics providing medical
OL,9,Fassistance to Mr Webber and Ms
OL,10,FO'Malley Kumar and placing both in
OL,11,Fbody bags.
OL,13,FSpecial constables are volunteer
OL,14,Fpolice officers with the same powers,
OL,15,Funiform and responsibilities as
OL,16,Fregular officers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FMs Craner told the inquiry: "It
OL,7,Fcertainly indicates that we should
OL,8,Fexplore whether there is more that we
OL,9,Fshould do at different points in an
OL,10,Finvestigation to restrict access (to
OL,11,Fcomputer systems)."
OL,13,FShe said she did not believe devices
OL,14,Fowned by Skenderaj had been seized and
OL,15,Fthat he was "offered an interview but
OL,16,Fdeclined".
OL,26,@nD@]OUsD@SO]wD@MOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FThe inquiry has heard that Skenderaj
OL,7,Fresigned from Nottinghamshire Police
OL,8,Fafter viewing images related to the
OL,9,Fattacks while at his home, with no
OL,10,Fpolicing purpose.
OL,12,FA Nottinghamshire Police constable was
OL,13,Falso disciplined in January 2024 after
OL,14,Fbreaching policing standards by
OL,15,Faccessing information about Calocane
OL,16,Fand sending a "degrading" WhatsApp
OL,17,Fmessage described as lacking any
OL,18,Fempathy in its description of victims'
OL,19,Finjuries.
OL,26,@xD@OOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FEmails read to the inquiry on Tuesday
OL,7,Fincluded one from a PDS officer who
OL,8,Fsaid: "If we start looking, there will
OL,9,Fbe countless officers that have looked
OL,10,Fwithout a policing purpose."
OL,12,FThe email, sent by a detective
OL,13,Fsergeant, suggested that one option
OL,14,Fwould be to undertake system audits,
OL,15,Fwhich a more senior officer rejected,
OL,16,Fsaying it would be a "massive" task.
OL,26,@pD@GOUrD@\O]xD@VOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FMr Webber's mother, Emma Webber, last
OL,7,Fmonth called for access to footage
OL,8,Fwithout a policing purpose to be
OL,9,Fconsidered a criminal matter and "for
OL,10,Fall these matters to be fully reopened
OL,11,Fand properly investigated".
OL,13,FDuring her evidence to the inquiry, Ms
OL,14,FCraner was asked if an audit of who
OL,15,Faccessed the footage had begun last
OL,16,Fmonth as a result of a complaint.
OL,18,FMs Craner said: "It hasn't yet
OL,19,Fcommenced but certainly the decision
OL,20,Fhas been made.
OL,26,@qD@bOUsD@ZO]zD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,F"The direction that I was given was
OL,7,Fthat we wouldn't conduct that audit
OL,8,Fourselves."
OL,10,FMs Craner was asked why it had taken
OL,11,Funtil March this year to decide to
OL,12,Fconduct an audit, when Nottinghamshire
OL,13,FPolice had known since September 2023
OL,14,Fthat a special constable had watched
OL,15,Fvideo from the attacks without a
OL,16,Flegitimate purpose.
OL,18,FShe said: "In hindsight what I should
OL,19,Fhave done is approach my line manager
OL,20,Fto ask for resource to undertake that
OL,21,Faudit."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@KO]zD@KOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FMr Ivory added: "The inevitable result
OL,7,Fis that until this audit is completed
OL,8,Fand any requisite disciplinary action
OL,9,Ftaken, there could be officers or
OL,10,Fpolice staff who viewed this footage
OL,11,Fillegitimately still serving couldn't
OL,12,Fthere?"
OL,14,FMs Craner answered: "Yes."
OL,16,FInquiry chairwoman Deborah Taylor
OL,17,Fasked Ms Craner if it would be
OL,18,Fpossible for permission to be given to
OL,19,Fa senior investigating officer so
OL,20,F"only those who needed to could have
OL,21,Faccess to the most sensitive material".
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@GO]vD@UOUvD@ZO]|D@AOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FMs Taylor also said that sensitive
OL,7,Fmaterial seemed to be "something that
OL,8,Fpeople feel that they have, in a
OL,9,Fsense, a right to view because of
OL,10,Fcuriosity."
OL,12,FMs Craner replied: "I think a small
OL,13,Fnumber of people have been shown to do
OL,14,Fthat."
OL,16,FMs Taylor interjected: "I suppose
OL,17,Fwe'll see with the audit won't we, how
OL,18,Fsmall that is."
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@KO]tD@TOUvD@FO]xD@XOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
