CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776258665
OL,3,COfficer viewed graphic images of two
OL,4,Cstudents stabbed by triple killer
OL,6,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,7,Fand three counts of attempted murder,
OL,8,Fis detained indefinitely in a high
OL,9,Fsecurity hospital after prosecutors
OL,10,Faccepted his not guilty pleas to
OL,11,Fmurder at his sentencing at Nottingham
OL,12,Fcrown court in January 2024.
OL,14,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
